<TITLE>
Pukwudgies, little people of the Algonquian tribes (Pukwudgie, Puckwudgie, Bagwajinini) 
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Pukwudgies, mythological Native American little people
from the folklore of the eastern Algonquian tribes.">
